data.description: Welcome to this charming single-family home located in a coveted gated neighborhood in the Stonechase subdivision with access to top-rated schools. Situated on a fully fenced in .51 acre lot, this spacious property offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Boasting 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, this home is ideal for families needing more space and room for activities. Enjoy the serenity of the surroundings and the security of a gated community just under $600,000. This property presents a rare opportunity for buyers seeking a dream home in a sought-after location highlighting tall ceilings, a relaxing back patio with a fireplace, large kitchen area and a refreshed fully fenced in yard for your children and animals.
